There are loads of covers of this on the net, but they're mostly in Japanese. The 
only English guy that covered it was kind enough to point me in the direction of a 
site that gave the chords, but they were matched to the kana, and the kana only. I 
realized that'd only be useful if you already knew the lyrics, and it's harder to 
learn that way, so I took the general chords, and wrote them to where I thought 
they fit best on the romanized lyrics. In a nutshell - the chords should match the 
syllables of the song perfectly/near perfectly. I left the rap part out, because 
that was a lot harder to do. While certainly not the first tab I've ever done, 
this is the first tab I've authored and uploaded, so excuse me if this block of 
text is against convention!

Any corrections, compliments, constructive criticisms to darkwaif@gmail.com.
